Invocation Name: westwood view
des: Ask Westwood View Calendar for daily events to help with quick planning of your day as an employee at Westwood View. Starting with the daily cafeteria menu, just ask "Westwood View" what's for lunch, to help you decide if you want to eat in the cafeteria or go out for lunch. Coming soon, community calendar events.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
